<a href="/wiki/Guil%C3%A1_Naquitz_Cave" title="Guilá Naquitz Cave">Guilá Naquitz Cave</a> in <a href="/wiki/Oaxaca" title="Oaxaca">Oaxaca</a>, <a href="/wiki/Mexico" title="Mexico">Mexico</a> is the site of early <a href="/wiki/Domestication#plants" title="Domestication">domestication</a> of several food crops, including <a href="/wiki/Teosinte" class="mw-redirect" title="Teosinte">teosinte</a> (an ancestor of maize).<sup id="cite_ref-benz_3-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-benz-3">[3]</a></sup></div>
